text: Laura Angélica Rojas Hernández (born 26 December 1975) is a Mexican politician. She is a member of the PAN. She was also the President of the Chamber of Deputies. She was a Senator from 2012 to 2018. During her ternure as Senator, she was the Chairwoman of the Foreign Affairs Comittee. Laura Rojas was elected President of the Chamber of Deputies on September 5, 2019. ==References== Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:Politicians from Mexico City Category:Presidents of the Chamber of Deputies (Mexico)
title: Laura Rojas Hernández
